description:
Seirin High School makes it into the semifinals of the Winter Cup. They defeated Toô Gakuen, featuring Aomine, and Yosen, featuring Murasakibara, both from the "Generation of Miracles," causing Seirin to be one of the more noticed schools.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: I`m Just Going at Full Strength
Je joue à fond, c`est tout
全力でやってるだけなんで
